## SavedObjectsImportRetry.duplicate property

Resolve an import conflict by creating a duplicate object with a new (undefined) originId. Note: this attribute is mutually-exclusive with `overwrite`<!-- -->. If both are enabled, `overwrite` takes precedence.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
duplicate?: boolean;
```
